@node Main "Angoes - Documentation"

                              'Angoes' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Angoes' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played on an 8 by 8 tile board, the idea is
to align 3 or more of the coloured angles so they are pointing in the same
direction. The catch is that the angles can only point in 2 directions:
either left and right or up and down, depending on how they are placed.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
